Paper: hep-th/9805062

Date: 1998-05-11

Title: A Proposal for Low Energy Dilaton

Comments: 4 pages, a talk given at PASCOS-98 (Northeastern, Mar.22-29, 98)

We propose a systematic way of introducing the (nongravitational) low energydilaton and a scheme for spontaneous breaking of scale symmetry (SBSS) isexplained.